  </fr:frontmatter>
  <fr:mainmatter><html:p>A set <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00MH.xml" title="countable set" addr="jms-00MH" type="local">countable</fr:link> if and only if the disjoint union <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A+{\mathopen {}\left  [1\right  ]\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00ME.xml" title="enumerable set" addr="jms-00ME" type="local">enumerable</fr:link>.</html:p>
 
   
