              <fr:mainmatter><html:p>Any non-empty subset of an <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00ME.xml" title="enumerable set" addr="jms-00ME" type="local">enumerable</fr:link> set is <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00ME.xml" title="enumerable set" addr="jms-00ME" type="local">enumerable</fr:link>.</html:p>
 
   
