          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>A <html:em><html:strong>countable set</html:strong></html:em> is one that is either empty or <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00ME.xml" title="enumerable set" addr="jms-00ME" type="local">enumerable</fr:link>.</html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
